# Open Brain Memory Rules

## Auto-Save Triggers (Always Capture)
- Key decisions/trade-offs: `capture_thought content="Decided X over Y because Z" type=decision`
- Bugs found: `capture_thought content="Bug: [desc]" type=bug tags=["fix"]`
- Features/tasks: `capture_thought content="[plan]" type=task`
- Ideas/reference: `type=idea/reference`

## Ask Before Save
Before major changes/plans: